parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake failure can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities, as the vehicle may not be able to stop or slow down in time to avoid collisions.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
extended stopping distance
brakes lock up
ABS system malfunctions
loss of braking power
grinding or pulsing sensations when applying brakes
brake light stays on
and difficulty stopping on wet or slippery surfaces.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Windshield wiper failure can reduce visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially during rain or snow.
symptoms: Intermittent windshield wiper failure
wipers stop working while driving
and wipers only work when the wire connector is wiggled.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: ABS system failure can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities, as the vehicle may not be able to stop or slow down in time to avoid collisions.
symptoms: ABS system malfunctions
extended stopping distance
brakes lock up
and loss of braking power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wipers can cause reduced visibility during inclement weather, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Windshield wipers work intermittently
stop in the middle of the windshield
or fail to work at all
sometimes requiring manual intervention to restart.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Spontaneous Shattering of Rear Window Glass
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the rear window glass can cause distraction, loss of visibility, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: The rear window glass shatters suddenly
without any apparent reason or warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to not retract properly, which can lead to accidents or injuries in the event of a crash, as the occupants may not be properly restrained.
symptoms: The seat belt does not retract
the seat belt hangs loosely
the seat belt pops open unexpectedly
the shoulder strap does not pull tight
the seat belt buckle is inoperative.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power door locks can cause inconvenience and potentially lead to safety issues if the doors become unlocked while driving.
symptoms: The power door locks fail to operate.
